VIII. CONCLUSION
In this paper, we proposed the method to adaptively set DC of LoRa node considering the packet collisions and surrounding environment using radio environment database. In our proposed method, DC of each node was adapted by using ACK communication from the LoRa gateway. The simulation results showed that the proposed method can reduce the interference time ratio and the packet loss rate less than the required values and contribute to the improvement of communication efÔ¨Åciency.

